<title>UK: BOE forecasts 1.3 bln stg shortage, offers help.</title>
<headline>BOE forecasts 1.3 bln stg shortage, offers help.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1996-08-20</dateline>
<text>
<p>The Bank of England offered the UK money market an early round of assistance after forecasting a liquidity shortage of around 1.3 billion stg.</p>
<p>The Bank invited money market operators to offer band 1 and 2 bills and offered an unrestricted bill/floating rate gilt repo to September 4 and 5.</p>
